.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/implementation-summary.md:97:2. **The current public front door still reaches a resolver beneath the spec tree.** The P0 remediation must land before this harness becomes a durable CI dependency.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/implementation-summary.md:98:3. **The drift exit-policy boundary remains open.** Lane C must report drift distinctly; the operator must decide whether the benchmark or separate drift-CI job owns the non-zero process signal.
