.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/plan.md:285:1. Set `SPECKIT_COMPILED_ROUTING=0` and verify fleet-wide legacy serving.
