.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/011-runtime-engine/plan.md:206:- [x] Hub is P4a-bound (compiled `selectedPolicy`) and the fence epoch is known.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/011-runtime-engine/plan.md:207:- [x] Frozen-scorer digests re-verified; canary green for the target hub.
