.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/011-runtime-engine/checklist.md:61:- [x] CHK-020 [P0] The engine returns a normalized decision and defers on off-signal prompts.
