.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/plan.md:204:| Dependency | Type | Status | Impact if Blocked |
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/plan.md:207:| Authoritative contracts in `spec.md` and `decision-record.md` | Internal | Available | Dependent phases must not invent alternate fallback or eligibility rules |
