    10	// Otherwise `resolveRoute` returns null and the caller keeps legacy routing.
    11	// This makes the cutover reversible two ways — unset the flag (fleet-wide) or
    12	// flip a hub's serving authority back to 'legacy' (per hub) — and inert by
    13	// default, so merely shipping this code changes nothing at runtime.
    14	
